Management Training Consultant
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/01 07:31:20
Ref. JB3046189
Job Description
Successful Training Consultancy seeks HR Guru/Management Training Consultant to join its Dubai office.
Skills
With clients all over the Middle & Far East, Europe and Africa this Training and Management Consultancy has a fantastic reputation in the market.
An extremely high retention rate, fantastic multinational clients, great work life balance and truly professional Consultants make this an employer of choice.
The role is to provide exceptional soft skills training and consulting to major multinational businesses and you will design and deliver bespoke training programs.
Candidates sought for this role must be of the highest caliber and will in return receive an excellent benefits package with a longer term equity offering.
We require:
- An Arabic speaker, able to travel to Saudi easily
- At least 5 years industry HR/Training experience within a top multinational business or industry experience coupled with consulting
- A highly polished and well presented individual with excellent Arabic and English skills
- Educated to a MINIMUM level of Masters degree
- Excellent presentation skills
- Experience of providing training in soft skills
Education
Masters Degree
